    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bindings of the style associated with Jean Grolier generally characterized by geometric patterns and arabesques, sometimes colored.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
